{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban employers from making changes to employment contracts once signed",
        "additional_details": "In recent times we have seen how many companies reduce benefits such as paid breaks or over-time payments. We think the Government should introduce protections for workers, so that employers are banned from making any changes to employment contracts once they are signed.",
        "background": "We call on the Government to introduce new protections to prevent employers changing the employment contracts once the employee has signed their employment contract.",
